 class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上次報名冬天去，話路程遠咗，要收附加費喎，佢哋話一係你喺南半球出發，會平啲。<br />\n<br />\n我一嘢屌鳩佢，咁咪好撚熱囉，我就係唔想咁熱先冬天去啫，南半球夏天咁熱，我去嚟把撚咩！！"},{"pid":"bc3ff911ed6c474e45ebcbae11ab2265a92df09e","tid":87730,"uid":44513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冬天去無咁熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上次報名冬天去，話路程遠咗，要收附加費喎，佢哋話一係你喺南半球出發，會平啲。<br />\n<br />\n我一嘢屌鳩佢，咁咪好撚熱囉，我就係唔想咁熱先冬天去啫，南半球夏天咁熱，我去嚟把撚咩！！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔介意唔係直航可以去月球轉機，會平d,不過只可以初一出發"},{"pid":"985fa2859277e96476d4050572e5ac67843fb910","tid":87730,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一早比蝗攻陷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a301ea6bc43fb8c7558f8c34ed253456a323737e","tid":87730,"uid":18913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"一定要查太陽油"},{"pid":"e22ea386a5fc076391b0a101504db21a9ad185fe","tid":87730,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定要查太陽油</blockquote><br />\n太陽眼鏡都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad63dadbe4195a4d62ba534493e0fe6ecd2206e2","tid":87730,"uid":43833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:14:58.000Z","msg":"仲好講，上次去到撞正天狗食日，爭d比隻衰狗食q埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc9c079896cfb765fe01e069f9b2e590da72ce2","tid":87730,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:20:47.000Z","msg":"屌 d野食又貴又難食<br />\n隻太陽蛋煎到燶曬都夠膽拎俾客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f416b7e8ddc93700283e19843f37eeecc572368e","tid":87730,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score